ScenarioHeader.Title: BKPF Incremental Recon

ScenarioDataSource.SQL_Text:
SELECT DISTINCT
MAX ( CONCAT ( CDHDR.UDATE, CDHDR.UTIME ) ) OVER (PARTITION BY CDPOS.TABKEY ) AS DATETIME,
CDPOS.CHNGIND,
BKPF.*
FROM "SAPECD"."CDHDR" CDHDR
INNER JOIN "SAPECD"."CDPOS" CDPOS
ON CDPOS.OBJECTCLAS = CDHDR.OBJECTCLAS
AND CDPOS.CHANGENR = CDHDR.CHANGENR
AND CDPOS.TABNAME = 'BKPF'
INNER JOIN "SAPECD"."BKPF" BKPF
ON CDPOS.OBJECTID = CONCAT ( CONCAT ( CONCAT ( BKPF.MANDT, BKPF.BUKRS ), BKPF.BELNR ), BKPF.GJAHR )
AND CDPOS.TABKEY = CONCAT ( CONCAT ( CONCAT ( BKPF.MANDT, BKPF.BUKRS ), BKPF.BELNR ), BKPF.GJAHR )
WHERE CDHDR.OBJECTCLAS = 'BELEG'
  AND ( CDHDR.UDATE >= '{GET_LAST_SUC_RUN( 1432, FDR, yyyyMMdd )}' )
  
ORDER BY BKPF.BUKRS, BKPF.BELNR, BKPF.GJAHR

SELECT DISTINCT
MAX ( CONCAT ( CDHDR.UDATE, CDHDR.UTIME ) ) OVER (PARTITION BY CDPOS.TABKEY ) AS DATETIME,
CDPOS.CHNGIND,
BKPF.*
FROM "SAP_TABLES"."PUBLIC"."CDHDR" CDHDR
INNER JOIN "SAP_TABLES"."PUBLIC"."CDPOS" CDPOS
ON CDPOS.OBJECTCLAS = CDHDR.OBJECTCLAS
AND CDPOS.CHANGENR = CDHDR.CHANGENR
AND CDPOS.TABNAME = 'BKPF'
INNER JOIN "SAP_TABLES"."PUBLIC"."BKPF" BKPF
ON CDPOS.OBJECTID = CONCAT ( CONCAT ( CONCAT ( BKPF.MANDT, BKPF.BUKRS ), BKPF.BELNR ), BKPF.GJAHR )
AND CDPOS.TABKEY = CONCAT ( CONCAT ( CONCAT ( BKPF.MANDT, BKPF.BUKRS ), BKPF.BELNR ), BKPF.GJAHR )
WHERE CDHDR.OBJECTCLAS = 'BELEG'
  AND ( CDHDR.UDATE >= '{GET_LAST_SUC_RUN( 1432, FDR, yyyyMMdd )}' )
  
ORDER BY BKPF.BUKRS, BKPF.BELNR, BKPF.GJAHR
